{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - equipment1","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01d2bnrq017t1mi7","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - equipo1","system":{"description":"<p><strong>Equipo de Astuto</strong></p><p>Ropas ligeras y cómodas / Un set de pequeños cuchillos que escondo por doquier / Cartas, estampas y otros objetos falsos / Algunas monedas y joyas completamente falsas / Un Volumen de Enciclopedia de la famosa Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana, la cual siempre me revela lo que necesito saber.</p>"}}},"contentKey":"equipment1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","sequence":1,"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","sortOrder":1,"slot":"equipment1"}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Cunning's Equipment</strong></p><p>Comfortable and light clothes / A set of small knives that I hide everywhere / Cards, stamps, and other counterfeit objects / Some completely fake coins and jewelry / A volume of the famous Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana Encyclopedia, which always reveals what I need to know.</p>","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","translationKey":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat.equipment1"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"btmacheq00000001"}
{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - equipment2","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"01d2bnrq017t1mi7","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - equipo2","system":{"description":"<p><strong>Equipo de Malicioso</strong></p><p>Ropas desgastadas y maltrechas / Una daga larga y afilada / Un viejo palo para fingir estar ciego / Una vieja bolsa con un agujero en ella / Un saco lleno de chatarra que recolecto mientras robo.</p>"}}},"contentKey":"equipment1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","sequence":1,"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","sortOrder":2,"slot":"equipment2"}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Sly's Equipment</strong></p><p>Worn-out and lived-in clothes / A long, sharp knife / An old stick to pretend to be blind / An old purse with a hole in it / A sack full of junk that I collect while thieving.</p>","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","translationKey":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat.equipment2"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"btmacheq00000002"}
